headline: Weyerhaeuser Announces Appointment of Rick Beckwitt to Board of Directors
summary: Weyerhaeuser Company (NYSE: WY) today announced the appointment of Richard "Rick" Beckwitt, former president, chief executive officer and director of Lennar Corporation, to the company's board of directors. His appointment is effective immediately.

headline: Louisiana-Pacific: A Tale Of 2 Markets
summary: Louisiana-Pacific is the largest manufacturer of engineered wood siding in North America and second-largest producer of oriented strand board on the continent. Learn more on LPX stock here.
